@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_shvwoo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.43 - v2 + 0.39) * (tmp + 0.96 - v0 + 0.24)))
    v1 = v2
    v2 = (0.05 - wp.abs(0.41))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.58 + v2 + 0.35)) - (wp.cos(v2 + 0.40) - 0.07))
    data[tid] = v0
